{"name": "pipemake", "metadata": {"name": "pipemake", "version": "1.1.5", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": "https://pipemake.readthedocs.io/en/latest/", "dependencies": [], "summary": "Pipemake: A pipeline creation tool using Snakemake", "upload_time": 1732299382}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  Conda Upload: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/upload_conda.yml/badge.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/upload_conda.yml\n    ```\n  Coverage: |-\n    ```{image} https://codecov.io/gh/kocherlab/pipemake/branch/main/graph/badge.svg\n    :alt: Coverage\n    :target: https://codecov.io/gh/kocherlab/pipemake\n    ```\n  Documentation: |-\n    ```{image} https://readthedocs.org/projects/pipemake/badge/?version=latest\n    :alt: Documentation Status\n    :target: https://pipemake.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest\n    ```\n  LICENSE: |-\n    ```{image} https://anaconda.org/kocherlab/pipemake/badges/license.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/blob/main/LICENSE\n    ```\n  PyPI Upload: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/python-publish.yml/badge.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/python-publish.yml\n    ```\n  Stable version: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/kocherlab/pipemake?label=stable\n    :alt: Stable version\n    :target: https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/releases/\n    ```\n  conda: |-\n    ```{image} https://anaconda.org/kocherlab/pipemake/badges/version.svg\n    :target: https://anaconda.org/kocherlab/pipemake\n    ```\n  github ci: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=main\n    :alt: Continuous integration status\n    :target: https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/actions/workflows/ci.yml\n    ```\n---\n\n{{ Stable version }} {{ Documentation }} {{ github ci }} {{ Coverage }} {{ conda }} {{ Conda Upload }} {{ PyPI Upload }} {{ LICENSE }}\n\n# Pipemake\n\nPipemake is a lightweight, flexible, and easy-to-use tool for creating and managing [Snakemake](https://snakemake.readthedocs.i/) pipelines. It was designed with two primary goals:\n\n1. Provide a collection of pre-built and easy to modify bioinformatic pipelines with an enphasis on genomics and social behavior analysis\n2. Provide a user-friendly interface for creating and managing pipelines with minimal programming experience\n\n## Getting Pipemake\n\n### Mamba\n\n```bash\nconda install -n base -c conda-forge mamba\nmamba create -c conda-forge -c bioconda -c kocherlab -n pipemake pipemake\n```\n\n## Issues\n\n1. Check the [docs](https://pipemake.rtfd.io/).\n2. Search the [issues on GitHub](https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/issues) or open a new one.\n\n## License\n\nPipemake is licensed under the MIT license. See the [LICENSE](https://github.com/kocherlab/pipemake/blob/main/LICENSE) file for details.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "pipemake.singularityIO", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "pipemake.singularityIO.checkSingularity", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "pipemake.singularityIO.Singularity", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "pipemake.singularityIO.Singularity.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "url", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "singularity_path", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pipemake.singularityIO.Singularity.processURL", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pipemake.singularityIO.Singularity.download", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "retur